From aaf96b10474bb3c9214ac12073bb2c9b8e6a22cd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: YTing46 <q36141367@gs.ncku.edu.tw>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 20:48:14 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 01/21] riscv: sophgo: add SG2002 C906L RPMsg dual-core stack
 for Milk-V Duo256M

Port the CVITEK/Sophgo dual-core (big core <-> C906L little core)
communication stack from the vendor Linux 5.10 SDK to mainline 7.0:

- rtos_cmdqu mailbox command-queue core under drivers/soc/cvitek/
- cvi_sg2002_c906l_remoteproc: boot/control the C906L coprocessor
- cvi_rpmsg_shmem: shared-memory virtio RPMsg transport
- sg2002-milkv-duo256m.dts board devicetree
- wire up Kconfig/Makefile and enable in riscv defconfig

